list.description: Disembodied, unintelligible voices of Brent and Eloise (Sawyer will deliver this asset)

Before I arrived in this level, I saw: 
- The user select screen of the game. 
- I clicked on Brent and saw the user account try to load. 
- An error message appeared:

(warning emoji)⚠️ Startup cannot continue because of a problem at: 

C:\Users\Dad\Documents\Work\Asphodel\Echo.exe

Click OK to open the Agave Recovery Wizard. 

- I clicked OK and entered the level.
The occasional chair, cactus, &c floats through the inaccessible part of the level (not a priority in the build for Rachel).
